<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Keres</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-16 17:54:47</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>About the mask and faction boosts. The mask doesnt have it's own faction, rather, it gives boosts and penalties to your existing faction standings when the illusion is in effect. For instance, if you dont want to be KoS in Neriak, dont kill a bunch of guards and think you can activate the mask and go untouched. It wont work and you will die a horrible death. On the other hand, this mask can be used to boost faction high enough to do the concordance of research quest in S. Ro, boosting faction enough to be non-KoS even without the illusion, at least in Neriak. Just my two coppers.</font></td></tr></table>
