<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Grishnakk</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-15 14:22:31</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>   Okay, I'll try to clear up some of these rumors cause they are just annoying to listen too =P.  Item is Face Slot +13 cha +7 SV Magic. Item is usuable by all classes that can play a Rogue or a Bard. Meaning All, so don't ask can a gnome too? Effect is available at Lvl 15 and is activated by wearing the Mask and going to your invintory Screen and right click it while your wearing it. Item is a COMMON drop off of the Assassian Undead Froglok in Lower Guk on the Dead Side in the Lower Tower area of the Zone. The room he spawns in is fondly called the Ass/Sup room as the Supplier Froglok spawns there also which drops a nice weight reduction backpack which reduces the weight of items in the bag by I believe 70%. If your a Rogue Hide and Sneak your way there I believe you get sneak at 4 or so... and now you ask "they are undead won't they see thru my Rogue invis?" No they do not...Only Cetain NAMED Frogloks can see thru Invis and none of them are along the way to the Ass/Sup room. Also the Assassian and the Supplier can't see thru it either. Bards I have never played so I have little ideas for you other than to beg for a ITU from a Pally or Cleric and then camp in the room and have the people there message you when it is dropped. FACTIONS... With this you will be able to enter all evil cities EXCEPT Cabalis as everyone is KOS to them (Lizards that is). Pending that you do not Worship a Good god. if you do you will die unless you've been especially working on your Factions. I have tried to be as complete as possible to cut off and questions. I hope I have been of help. Happy Hunting.<BR>
<BR>
                           Grishnakk<BR>
